<li><a href="http://isotropic.org/uw/date/" class="external text" title="http://isotropic.org/uw/date/" rel="nofollow">Another Julian Day calculator with conversions to many other calendars</a> valid from <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="0100-01-01"><a href="/wiki/January_1" title="January 1">1 January</a> <a href="/wiki/100" title="100">100</a></span> proleptic Gregorian calendar</li>
<li><a href="http://pc-calculator.sourceforge.net/" class="external text" title="http://pc-calculator.sourceforge.net/" rel="nofollow">Pc-Calculator, Julian Date Calculator</a></li>
</ul>


